sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor NguoiDung as NguoiNopDon
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgSvc as OrganizationService
participant JoinDb as Mongo_JoinApplication
participant MemberDb as Mongo_Membership

Note over NguoiDung,MemberDb: Chặng 2 - Nộp đơn và xử lý ngoại lệ
NguoiDung->>Client: Gửi đơn tham gia tổ chức
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/join-applications
Gateway->>OrgSvc: Forward request
OrgSvc->>JoinDb: Validate form + lưu pending

alt Reviewer duyệt
  OrgSvc->>MemberDb: Tạo membership active
  OrgSvc-->>Client: 200 duyệt thành công
else Đơn trùng hoặc dữ liệu sai
  OrgSvc-->>Client: 400/409
else Không đủ quyền duyệt
  OrgSvc-->>Client: 403
end
